** ** We are currently seeking an experienced ** Senior Software Engineer ** to join a fast growing SaaS startup. You will have the opportunity to work on a variety of exciting projects that leverage the latest technologies, including Single Page Applications (SPAs), React, Svelte, .NET Core, Azure, DevOps, AI and Flutter.   
  
The engineers are currently dealing with a number of challenges, including
making the platform more scalable and performant, as well as adding additional
features to the platform.  
You will be responsible for designing, developing, and implementing complex
cloud-based solutions using a variety of technologies, including React, Svelte
C#, .NET Core, Typescript, Kubernetes, Docker and Azure. Working closely with
the other engineers in the team, you will build new features for the flagship
SaaS product. This year will also see them investigating and implementing
Arteficial Intelligence into their product as well as building a mobile
version of their platform (Flutter).  
  
** To be successful in this role ** , you should have experience with:   
  
\- Containerised, Event Driven Architecture  
\- C# / .NET COre  
\- React, Svelte and/or Typescript  
\- Azure & Azure DevOps  
  
Nice to have: Storybook for UI build/test and Flutter for Mobile development.  
You should be a self-starter with a passion for learning and staying up-to-
date with emerging technologies. You should also have excellent communication
and collaboration skills, as this role involves working closely with other
developers, project managers, and clients.  
As an employer, they are committed to providing our team with the support they
need to succeed.  
  
